          "rangeEnd": 1823,
          "markText": "永远别去召唤自己控制不了的力量。",
          "colorStyle": 2,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1739747707,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2025-02-17 07:15:07",
          "chapterUid": 4,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300119145&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1807&rangeEnd=1823",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a24329f0813ab950ag015395?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1807&rangeEnd=1823"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "3300119145_4_26400-26438",
          "range": "26400-26438",
          "rangeStart": 26400,
          "rangeEnd": 26438,
          "markText": "最后的第十一章谈论的是这套新信息网络如何左右全球民主与极权社会之间的权力平衡",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1738328508,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2025-01-31 21:01:48",
          "chapterUid": 4,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300119145&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=26400&rangeEnd=26438",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a24329f0813ab950ag015395?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=26400&rangeEnd=26438"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "3300119145_4_26242-26267",
          "range": "26242-26267",
          "rangeStart": 26242,
          "rangeEnd": 26267,
          "markText": "第十章则探讨了非生物信息网络可能如何影响极权主义。",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1738328471,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2025-01-31 21:01:11",
          "chapterUid": 4,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300119145&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=26242&rangeEnd=26267",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a24329f0813ab950ag015395?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=26242&rangeEnd=26267"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "3300119145_4_26052-26078",
          "range": "26052-26078",
          "rangeStart": 26052,
          "rangeEnd": 26078,
          "markText": "第九章讨论的是民主国家如何处理非生物信息网络的兴起。",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1738328455,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2025-01-31 21:00:55",
          "chapterUid": 4,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300119145&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=26052&rangeEnd=26078",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a24329f0813ab950ag015395?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=26052&rangeEnd=26078"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "3300119145_4_25909-25952",
          "range": "25909-25952",
          "rangeStart": 25909,
          "rangeEnd": 25952,
          "markText": "本书的第三部分“计算机政治学”探讨了不同类型的社会如何应对非生物信息网络的威胁与承诺。",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1738328439,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2025-01-31 21:00:39",
          "chapterUid": 4,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300119145&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=25909&rangeEnd=25952",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a24329f0813ab950ag015395?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=25909&rangeEnd=25952"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "3300119145_4_25430-25615",
          "range": "25430-25615",
          "rangeStart": 25430,
          "rangeEnd": 25615,
          "markText": "本书第二部分“非生物网络”讨论的是人类如今正在打造的新信息网络，重点关注人工智能兴起的政治意义。第六章到第八章讨论了世界各地近些年发生的例子（比如，2016—2017年社交媒体算法如何在缅甸煽动种族冲突），以解释人工智能与过去所有信息技术的不同之处。之所以例子大多取自21世纪10年代，而不是21世纪20年代，是因为我们对21世纪10年代的事件已经有了一些历史性的观点。",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1738328409,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2025-01-31 21:00:09",
          "chapterUid": 4,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300119145&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=25430&rangeEnd=25615",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a24329f0813ab950ag015395?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=25430&rangeEnd=25615"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "3300119145_4_24917-24971",
          "range": "24917-24971",
          "rangeStart": 24917,
          "rangeEnd": 24971,
          "markText": "历史真正研究的并不是“过去”，而是“变化”。历史能告诉我们什么是不变的、什么是变化的，以及事物又是如何变化的",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1738328334,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2025-01-31 20:58:54",
          "chapterUid": 4,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300119145&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=24917&rangeEnd=24971",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a24329f0813ab950ag015395?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=24917&rangeEnd=24971"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "3300119145_4_24052-24147",
          "range": "24052-24147",
          "rangeStart": 24052,
          "rangeEnd": 24147,
          "markText": "在第一部分，我最先考察的是对于大规模人类信息网络至关重要的两个概念：神话故事和官僚制度。在第二章与第三章，我描述了大规模信息网络（从古代王国到现代国家）是如何同时有赖于神话编造者与官僚制度的",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1738328289,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2025-01-31 20:58:09",
          "chapterUid": 4,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300119145&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=24052&rangeEnd=24147",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a24329f0813ab950ag015395?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=24052&rangeEnd=24147"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "3300119145_4_24377-24427",
          "range": "24377-24427",
          "rangeStart": 24377,
          "rangeEnd": 24427,
          "markText": "第四章的重点是谈论错误信息的问题，以及维持各种自我修正机制（例如独立司法、同行评议期刊）的好处与坏处",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1738328281,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2025-01-31 20:58:01",
          "chapterUid": 4,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300119145&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=24377&rangeEnd=24427",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a24329f0813ab950ag015395?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=24377&rangeEnd=24427"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "3300119145_4_24676-24714",
          "range": "24676-24714",
          "rangeStart": 24676,
          "rangeEnd": 24714,
          "markText": "第五章会以另一种对比来结束第一部分的历史讨论：分布式信息网络和集中式信息网络",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1738328271,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2025-01-31 20:57:51",
          "chapterUid": 4,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300119145&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=24676&rangeEnd=24714",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a24329f0813ab950ag015395?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=24676&rangeEnd=24714"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "3300119145_4_2394-2425",
          "range": "2394-2425",
          "rangeStart": 2394,
          "rangeEnd": 2425,
          "markText": "力量从来就不是个人努力的结果，人类的力量总是源于大批人的合作。",
          "colorStyle": 0,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1730721025,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2024-11-04 19:50:25",
          "chapterUid": 4,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300119145&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=2394&rangeEnd=2425",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a24329f0813ab950ag015395?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=2394&rangeEnd=2425"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "chapterUid": 19,
      "chapterTitle": "结语",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "3300119145_19_5189-5238",
          "range": "5189-5238",
          "rangeStart": 5189,
          "rangeEnd": 5238,
          "markText": "信息并不等于真理，信息的主要任务在于联结，而非呈现现实，而且史上的信息网络往往比较重视秩序而非真理",
